<HEADLINE> Philippines Senate Okays '99 National Budget </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, December 23 (Xinhua) -- The Senate of the Philippines
Wednesday ratified the national budget for 1999, capping its "year
of legislative work."
</P>
<P>
Senate President Marcelo Fernan said the approved budget of 585
billion pesos (14.63 billion U.S. dollars) could well be their
gift to the people for the Christmas season, a budget that
"addresses the issues of poverty."
</P>
