<HEADLINE> Stamp Sheetlet to Commemorate HK's Performance at Asian Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 23 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong Post will issue a
definitive stamp sheetlet on March 27, 1999 to commemorate the
outstanding performance by the athletes of the Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region in the 1998 Asian Games held in Bangkok.
</P>
<P>
This was announced by acting Postmaster General P C Luk here
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
This stamp sheetlet, which incorporates four definitive stamps,
will be sold at 9.7 HK dollars (1.24 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong athletes grabbed five gold, six silver and six bronze
medals in Bangkok, which represented the best ever performance by
any Hong Kong delegations at Asian Games. 
</P>
</TEXT>
