<HEADLINE> Shenzhen Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 23 (Xinhua) -- The Component Stock Index on
the Shenzhen Stock Exchange closed at 3,024.19 points today, down
28.43 points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
