</P>
<P>
The Parliament passed a resolution Monday requesting the
president to relieve the minister of his duties.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a meeting of the ruling National Resistance
Movement at the International Conference Center Tuesday, Museveni
said the privatization probe report of the Parliament was
superficial and not properly researched.
</P>
