Museveni would be breaking the Constitution if he does not take
action on Kuteesa.
</P>
<P>
One popular opinion is that Museveni would not take action
against this minister because his wife is the first lady's
sister.
</P>
<P>
However, Museveni has told the general public that the
government is never lack of political will to remove corrupt
officials from the ruling class. 
