<HEADLINE> Winds Drives American Yacht Back </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 22 (Xinhua) -- One of the three American
skippers left in the Around Alone around-the-world yacht race has
withdrawn his battered boat back toward South Africa after
pulling out of the race.
</P>
<P>
