<HEADLINE> Southern Chinese Province Preparing For Spring Transport Surge </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, December 23 (Xinhua) -- Transportation departments
in China's Guangdong Province have drawn up plans for the spring
period, the annual peak season, during the Spring Festival.
</P>
