transport by putting more buses and passengers trains and planes
into operation.
</P>
<P>
The number of passengers is expected to rise dramatically early
next year as more farmers, especially in the flood-hit areas come
to Guangdong looking for jobs.
</P>
<P>
It is predicted that 21 million people may be on the move
before Spring Festival, a rise of 4 percent over last Spring
Festival, and there may be more passengers after the festival.
</P>
