<HEADLINE> Biathlonist Dafovska Named Balkans' Athlete of 1998 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, December 22 (Xinhua) -- Olympic biathlon champion
Ekaterina Dafovska was named Balkan Athlete of the Year in the
BTA annual poll.
</P>
<P>
For the first time in the 26-year history of the poll, it is
won by a winter sports athlete.
</P>
<P>
